reviewText: I have seen alot of interviews of Beyonce's and I feel that this one was amazing. It really goes in depth because she tells you everything! You get inside stories that are wonderful!!!

THIS IS A GR8 BEYONCE DVD COLLECTION....IT SHOWS ALOT OF HER MUSIC VIDEO'S & STUFF....THIS IS A MUST FOR ANY TRUE "BEYONCE FAN"....YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPPOINTED AT ALL....GR8 MUSIC FROM A GREAT ARTIST....IT'S WORTH THE MONEY!!!!
I purchased this as a gift for a "collector" of Beyonce memorabilia. They liked it.
Beyonce is da best. She's in her own catergoie
It was a gift for a Beyonce fan. I didn't hear any negative comments

It's a great addition if you are a Beyonce fan. It is also great if you loved B'day because Beyonce shares a lot of information about making the album. A great conversation between Beyonce and her fans about her sophomore album!
Maybe I didn't pay close enough attention but I had no idea that this item was in Spanish. The title of the posting alone was a little misleading compared to how obvious it was when the item arrived.
Excellent compilation of interviews incorporated with music videos in a DVD. A very informative and entertaining selection by Beyonce too sweet herself.
This is not what I thought as far as content.  I thought there would be more music videos
If you're the ultimate Beyonc fan (which I am)then you'll enjoy this disc, it include footage not seen anywhere additional videos and just fun extras
I AM VERY MUCH A HUGE FAN OF HERS & 100% SATISFIED WITH THIS ITEM. THE DESCRIPTION WAS PERFECT & I HIGHLY RECOMMEND THIS SELLER TO OTHER CUSTOMERS!
This DVD was fun to watch! Its shorter then most Beyonc Documentaries but it was worth the cheap price. If your a Bey fan I would get it.
I really enjoy watch Beyonc video. It was fun to see Beyonc when she first come out again. I give the DVD a 5 star.
